  "description": "The Collision recipe at maximum harmonic complexity: proc3=Wavefolder with RingMod-adjacent behavior on the combined signal. Pulse src1 (PW=0.35, asymmetric) against Saw src2 at +6 semitones — the largest detune interval in this series, creating distinct beating and harmonic interaction. proc1=LP (1550 Hz, reso=0.45) shapes the Pulse into a rounded wedge; proc2=LP (540 Hz, reso=0.52, higher reso) gives the Saw a resonant midrange spike. The two resonant peaks collide in the mix. proc3=Wavefolder (4500 Hz) catches the combined peaks. fmDepth=0.3 (highest in this series). Poly4 for complex chord voicing. Mod: Env->FilterCutoff, LFO->srcMix (collision ratio shifts), Velocity->FilterReso, Aftertouch->FXMix.",
